      "text": "Hello\nIs there an easy way to adjust the size of the axis/labels so that units fit nicely in the canvas and tat we dont get the x10 cropped out like in my case? I know that there is a --left-margin option, but there is no --right-margin one.\nTIA\nScreenshot 2026-05-27 at 16.59.29948\u00d7152 30.9 KB",
